            "last_activity_date": 1295297100,
            "creation_date": 1295297100,
            "body": "<p>There is a Java port of the classic BLAS linear algebra libraries available at <\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://icl.cs.utk.edu/f2j/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://icl.cs.utk.edu/f2j/<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>I have not used this before, but it looks like it could be very useful.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 4717710,
